<Page title="About" description="About Ag Alewerks — Hand crafted ales by Silvia & Barry">
  <h1>About</h1>

  <p>
    Long ago, in a "previous life" both of us were medical laboratory professionals. Mixing
    reagents and growing bugs was something that I really enjoyed. Software development
    challenges and pay lured me away from the laboratory, but I have always sort of missed
    the precision of measuring, mixing, and testing.
  </p>

  <p>
    When I would yen for the good ol' days in the lab, Silvia would suggest that I start home
    brewing beer. It took hearing this coaxing many times before I realized it for the
    encouraging nudge that it truly represented.
  </p>

  <p>
    Eventually I started trolling Craigslist for used home brewing equipment. This is the
    result of that search and the start of this chronicle.
  </p>

  <figure>
    <img
